{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":8438,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153724,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158719,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161834,"text":"Hi, everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164525,"text":"Ban-gap-seum-ni-da."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166644,"text":"I'd like to share with you a little bit of me"},{"time":169478,"text":"playing my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171590,"text":"I might look successful and happy"},{"time":174279,"text":"being in front of you today,"},{"time":176377,"text":"but I once suffered from severe depression"},{"time":179463,"text":"and was in total despair."},{"time":181828,"text":"The violin, which meant everything to me,"},{"time":184933,"text":"became a grave burden on me."},{"time":187510,"text":"Although many people tried to comfort and encourage me,"},{"time":191236,"text":"their words sounded like meaningless noise."},{"time":195161,"text":"When I was just about to give everything up"},{"time":198523,"text":"after years of suffering,"},{"time":200886,"text":"I started to rediscover the true power of music."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206427,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":287924,"text":"In the midst of hardship,"},{"time":290776,"text":"it was the music that gave me -- that restored my soul."},{"time":296266,"text":"The comfort the music gave me"},{"time":298035,"text":"was just indescribable,"},{"time":299745,"text":"and it was a real eye-opening experience for me too,"},{"time":303909,"text":"and it totally changed my perspective on life"},{"time":307213,"text":"and set me free from the pressure"},{"time":309869,"text":"of becoming a successful violinist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314807,"text":"Do you feel like you are all alone?"},{"time":317946,"text":"I hope that this piece will touch and heal your heart,"},{"time":321505,"text":"as it did for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324016,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400051,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":408758,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410503,"text":"Now, I use my music to reach people's hearts"},{"time":414440,"text":"and have found there are no boundaries."},{"time":417119,"text":"My audience is anyone who is here to listen,"},{"time":420678,"text":"even those who are not familiar with classical music."},{"time":424926,"text":"I not only play at the prestigious classical concert halls"},{"time":429775,"text":"like Carnegie Hall and Kennedy Center,"},{"time":431710,"text":"but also hospitals, churches, prisons,"},{"time":435501,"text":"and restricted facilities for leprosy patients,"},{"time":439721,"text":"just to mention a few."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441687,"text":"Now, with my last piece, I'd like to show you"},{"time":446297,"text":"that classical music can be so much fun, exciting,"},{"time":449978,"text":"and that it can rock you."},{"time":452782,"text":"Let me introduce you to my brand new project,"},{"time":456210,"text":"\"Baroque in Rock,\""},{"time":457715,"text":"which became a golden disc most recently."},{"time":461407,"text":"It's such an honor for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463904,"text":"I think, while I'm enjoying my life as a happy musician,"},{"time":468145,"text":"I'm earning a lot more recognition than I've ever imagined."},{"time":472778,"text":"But it's now your turn."},{"time":476345,"text":"Changing your perspectives"},{"time":477816,"text":"will not only transform you but also the whole world."},{"time":481764,"text":"Just play your life with all you have,"},{"time":484247,"text":"and share it with the world."},{"time":486581,"text":"I really look forward to witnessing"},{"time":488406,"text":"a transforming world by you, TEDsters."},{"time":492351,"text":"Play your life, and stay tuned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":497410,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":727179,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}